race.description: Spry Civil Construction Mixed Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: GOLD BENZ (1) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (22.87) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record here winning two races. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from six attempts. Has ability and can bounce back. DAYNE'S CALAIS (7) is a talented type who notched his 20th career success when too good (19.55) at Angle Park last time. Expected to feature again. HUNTSMAN (8) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (17.36) at Mt Gambier. Has a good record at this journey. Has never missed the frame from six starts from this draw, including two wins. Expected to feature again. BLACK VIPER (2) looks an each-way chance.
